descriptionHtml:
This is not every item in the game, but it has many good weapons, all alchemy items, modded carry weight, god mod, money, spells, shouts, artifacts and enchantments also includes a set of crafting armor and an extra set to for a better set. Must have dlc or just edit and delete anything that begins with something else besides 00

To use do this
1. press the ` button to open commands
2. enter: bat all
Tada, you now have lots of great things.
(steps to help newbies)
1.)Download, probably in zip, might not be.
(1.5 If it is extract it)
2.)Insert into the Data folder
3.)Follow the first steps
